<title>
Uklanjanje i ugradnja audiouređaja
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A9F06001001">
<title>
Uklanjanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odspojite negativni kabel (-) s akumulatora.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite rešetku središnjeg otvora za provjetravanje. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A9306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite audiouređaj (1) s ploče s instrumentima nakon što ste skinuli 2 pričvrsna vijka (2).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odspojite konektore audiouređaja (3).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9F0004.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "63.065mm" ver = "03" gw = "199" gh = "162"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A9F06001002">
<title>
Ugradnja
</title>
<ptxt>
Obrnite postupak uklanjanja.
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
